      "act": "COLD OPEN",
      "estimated_duration_s": 11,
      "narration_text": "This is Liam, in for Bear. A classical harmonic oscillator of fixed energy traces an ellipse in position-momentum phase space. Its enclosed area is the action around one orbit.",
